Package hu.bme.mit.theta.grammar.dsl.gen

Class TypeBaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.grammar.dsl.gen.TypeBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
TypeListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class TypeBaseListener extends Object implements TypeListener
This class provides an empty implementation of TypeListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
